@startuml
actor User
participant "Subscription Management" as Subscription
participant "User Service" as UserService
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService

User -> Subscription : Navigate to Subscription Page
Subscription -> UserService : Retrieve Subscription Details
UserService -> Subscription : Return Current Subscription Info
User -> Subscription : Select Terminate Subscription
Subscription -> UserService : Confirm Action
UserService -> PaymentService : Process Termination
PaymentService -> UserService : Confirmation of Termination
UserService -> Subscription : Update User Profile
Subscription -> User : Confirmation of Cancellation
@enduml